  Organization             = {International Society for Optics and Photonics},
  Pages                    = {80470L--80470L},

  Abstract                 = {This article proposes an approach that enriches sensor data streams with semantic attributes so that these feeds have proper meaning. They are focused on semantics of detected event, event classification, relationships to other events, etc. Not so much focused on the locational semantics. It also presents 6 use cases. In the future they hope "to extend and bring the SSN-XG ontology work into [their] system".},
